			'<p><img class="aligncenter size-large" src="../file/2022/2/mad-world-5-0-alpha-test-709x418.jpg" alt="Mad World 5.0 Alpha Test" width="709" height="418" /></p>\r\n<p>Jandisoft is preparing for the next Alpha Test of its HTML5-based MMO Mad World. Scheduled to kick off on February 23, the test will last for five days ending on February 27. During this time, players will be helping to test all-new content including new quests for Acts 3 and 4, new dungeons, new skills, new mastery nodes, and more. Also included in the test will be general things like balancing and quality of life features.</p>\r\n<p>Those interested in taking part in the test can register for it now <a title="Mad World Website" href="https://www.madworldmmo.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">via the game‚Äôs homepage</a>. Anyone who participated in previous tests has no need to worry about registering again. They will be added automatically.</p>\r\n<p><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/AJ9OIs6Qhxo" title="YouTube video player" width="709" height="418" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"></iframe></p>',
