		description:
			'<p><img class="aligncenter size-large" src="../file/2022/2/phantasy-star-online-2-new-genesis-dark-falz-709x418.jpg" alt="Phantasy Star Online 2 New Genesis Dark Falz" width="709" height="418" /></p>\r\n<p><a title="Phantasy Star Online 2: New Genesis Game Page" href="../review/phantasy-star-online-2-new-genesis">Phantasy Star Online 2: New Genesis</a> players received some new content with the release of <a title="Phantasy Star Online 2 February 16 2022 Update" href="https://pso2.com/players/news/update20220216/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">today‚Äôs update</a>. While not a big update ‚Äì <a title="Phantasy Star Online 2: New Genesis February 2022 Update" href="../news/the-phantasy-star-online-2-new-genesis-february-update-arrived">that happened earlier this month</a> ‚Äì this one does introduce some new experiences for players in the form of the Dark Falz Interception Urgent Quest and the Vanford Laboratory Ruins High Rank Combat Sector. It also introduces some new gear and scratch ticket items for players to get their hands on.</p>\r\n<p>To participate in the new Urgent Quest, players will need to head to Central Aelio. They‚Äôll also need a battle power of 1898 or more to take the challenge on and meet the new boss Dark Falz. Players with a slightly lower battle power ‚Äì say around 1759 ‚Äì can access the new High Rank sector.</p>\r\n<p>As for the new scratch ticket, it has a bit of a desert theme with pastel colors and a layered style. The new gear features three new weapons, the Cinquem Spear, Cinquem Tails, and the Cinquem Bow.</p>\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet tw-align-center">\r\n<p dir="ltr" lang="en">Dark Falz strikes back! üî•üí´‚ú®<br />The all-new Urgent Quest arrives in <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/PSO2NGS?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#PSO2NGS</a> tomorrow, are you prepared? <a href="https://t.co/vLu8wnyCLc">pic.twitter.com/vLu8wnyCLc</a></p>\r\n‚Äî Phantasy Star Online 2 New Genesis - Global (@play_pso2) <a href="https://twitter.com/play_pso2/status/1493647731490967558?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 15, 2022</a></blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n<script src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js"></script>\r\n</p>',
